    <body>
        <header>
    <h1>Custom Program</h1>
        </header>

        <section>
    <h2>Warm-up Exercises</h2>
    <div>
        <h3>Exercise 1: Neck Stretch</h3>
        <p>Duration: 5 minutes</p>
        <p>Instructions: Sit or stand with your back straight. Slowly tilt your head towards your shoulder and hold for 10 seconds. Repeat on the other side.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h3>Exercise 2: Shoulder Shrugs</h3>
        <p>Duration: 5 minutes</p>
        <p>Instructions: Raise your shoulders up towards your ears and hold for a few seconds. Release and repeat 10 times.</p>
    </div>
        </section>

        <section>
    <h2>Strengthening Exercises</h2>
    <div>
        <h3>Exercise 1: Squats</h3>
        <p>Duration: 10 minutes</p>
        <p>Instructions: Stand with feet shoulder-width apart, lower your body as if sitting in a chair, and then return to standing. Repeat 15 times.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h3>Exercise 2: Leg Raises</h3>
        <p>Duration: 10 minutes</p>
        <p>Instructions: Lie on your back, lift one leg to a 45-degree angle and hold for 5 seconds, then lower. Repeat with the other leg.</p>
    </div>
        </section>

